<p local-id=3D"32ac38782ff1">The API Gateway here acts both as traditional =
API Gateway and AI Agent Gateway, using</p>
<ul local-id=3D"554976b5e6e0">
<li local-id=3D"0544ab166671">
<p local-id=3D"7340cd48bb6f">Kong as API Gateway, for authentication, HTTP =
routing</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4148d5b8a1f8">
<p local-id=3D"a6f844495af0">Agent Gateway as AI Gateway for A2A, MCP, etc<=
/p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"39a5b420df62" id=3D"AIAgentAPIGateway-DevelopmentEnvironmen=
t">Development Environment</h2>
<p local-id=3D"3a0ad0f4f40f">The endpoint is <code>https://dev-ai.omnisaas.=
cn/</code></p>
<p local-id=3D"49370c50d614">Enforced by Kong, for staging environment. It =
now only requires a static API key.</p>
<div id=3D"expander-1564603999" class=3D"expand-container">
<div id=3D"expander-control-1564603999" class=3D"expand-control">
<span class=3D"expand-control-icon"><img style=3D"vertical-align:middle;" c=
lass=3D"expand-control-image" src=3D"30b3942d298e5ebfb3735230f00f5dfd9bfc87=
dd5f3c96390e0233b2eb843ddc" width=3D"16" height=3D"16"></span><span class=
=3D"expand-control-text">Development API Key</span>
</div>
<div id=3D"expander-content-1564603999" class=3D"expand-content">
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-not=
e">
<span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-info=
rmation-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<p local-id=3D"188ec5056f1a">Current API key for staging is <code>963e75315=
b2ff4ddd39692c22604955fc521bc6474faf272cc22eb0c</code>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"376dc9e520dd">Please note that it may change any time when w=
e proceed with further development.</p>
<p local-id=3D"a86dfcf93783">Contact DevOps team if you have any concerns.<=
/p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"a57f2b7aebf2">you can pass it by following means</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">- in HT=
TP header, "apikey: ..."
- in Query String, https://..../...?apikey=3D...</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h2 local-id=3D"50fea30e8eec" id=3D"AIAgentAPIGateway-Exampleusage">Example=
 usage</h2>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">curl ht=
tps://dev-ai.omnisaas.cn/api/provider/qwen/v1/chat/completions  -H "apikey:=
 ..." \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "model": "qwen-plus",  ## pay attention to the model here
    "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "Hello"}]
  }'</pre>
</div>
</div>
