<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-not=
e">
<span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-info=
rmation-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<p local-id=3D"af87a627d35d">Please be advised, for the time being, above e=
ndpoint and paths in Agent Gateway are only integrated and support Chat API=
 (not Response API).</p>
<p local-id=3D"c8bac5eb60bd">Additionally, AQ (=E8=9A=82=E8=9A=81=E9=98=BF=
=E7=A6=8F) doesn=E2=80=99t support API access at the moment.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"7512654d2144"></p>
<div class=3D"panel" style=3D"background-color: #EAE6FF;border-color: #998D=
D9;border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"panelContent" style=3D"background-color: #EAE6FF;">
<p local-id=3D"af0a6750f0b5">Due to the nature of Agent Gateway, API routes=
 are not strictly mapped to upstream AI provider endpoints. That means, fol=
lowing paths work like</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence"># paths=
 after designated are just ignored in Agent Gateway,=20
#following paths are considered the same
/api/provider/&lt;provider&gt;/v1/chat/completions
/api/provider/&lt;provider&gt;/
/api/provider/&lt;provider&gt;/you/can/actually/put/anything/here

# for compatible with previous design,=20
# root path works like before and redirect request to qwen
# followings work in same way
/api/
/api/provider/=20
/api/provider/qwen
/api/provider/qwen/anything</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<h2 local-id=3D"4f688896585d" id=3D"AIAgentAPIGateway-Management">Managemen=
t</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"758339970cbc">
<li local-id=3D"c35b8a2a429c">
<p local-id=3D"0ffcaeee294e">environment: in k8s omnisaas staging cluster</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7fa49e1ff868">
<p local-id=3D"07746682b67b">namespace: <code>ai-demo</code></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5dd9eb7e3bc0">
<p local-id=3D"e749c00f6576">how to access agent-gateway ui</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a6a3a4a77ef4">
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">kubectl=
 -n ai-demo port-forward svc/agent-gateway --address 0.0.0.0 15000:15000
# now try accessing http://localhost:15000/</pre>
</div>
</div></li>
</ul>
    </div>
